      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEST FOR STEPS (1) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (17.68) but scored three back at this track (17.28). Returns to favourable track. Can atone. GLOW GIRL (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Common Chaos (17.50) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. JUNK YARD LORAIN (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 17.59 beating Zatara Mac. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Expecting another bold showing. BLUEY BRANN (4) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 1.75 lengths third (17.47) in a Grade 5 at this track.",
